    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "p1-items",
      "x": 80,
      "y": 178,
      "width": 750,
      "height": 250,
      "text": "1. Business entity formation (LLC or PLLC — telehealth-friendly state like FL, TX, or AZ)\n2. Medical Director / Prescribing Physician agreement ($2-5K/mo — MD/DO required)\n3. State medical board licensing (multi-state telehealth — consider compact states)\n4. DEA registration (required for certain controlled peptides & weight loss compounds)\n5. Pharmacy partnerships (certified U.S. 503A/503B compounding pharmacies — CRITICAL)\n6. HIPAA compliance (telehealth platform, encrypted comms, BAA with all vendors)\n7. Telemedicine platform setup (Healthie, Practice Better, or SimplePractice)\n8. Business bank account, merchant processing & accounting\n9. Legal review (FDA compliance for peptide marketing — CANNOT claim to treat/cure)\n10. Malpractice + general liability + cyber liability insurance (telehealth = cyber risk)",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "1. Business entity formation (LLC or PLLC — telehealth-friendly state like FL, TX, or AZ)\n2. Medical Director / Prescribing Physician agreement ($2-5K/mo — MD/DO required)\n3. State medical board licensing (multi-state telehealth — consider compact states)\n4. DEA registration (required for certain controlled peptides & weight loss compounds)\n5. Pharmacy partnerships (certified U.S. 503A/503B compounding pharmacies — CRITICAL)\n6. HIPAA compliance (telehealth platform, encrypted comms, BAA with all vendors)\n7. Telemedicine platform setup (Healthie, Practice Better, or SimplePractice)\n8. Business bank account, merchant processing & accounting\n9. Legal review (FDA compliance for peptide marketing — CANNOT claim to treat/cure)\n10. Malpractice + general liability + cyber liability insurance (telehealth = cyber risk)",
      "autoResize": true,
