    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "p2-items",
      "x": 80,
      "y": 518,
      "width": 750,
      "height": 280,
      "text": "1. Peptide protocol library (dosing, cycling, contraindications, monitoring)\n2. Signature programs/stacks design:\n   • Weight Management (Tirzepatide or Semaglutide — 12-week program)\n   • Anti-Aging Stack (NAD+, GHK-Cu, Epithalon)\n   • Recovery \"Wolverine\" Stack (BPC-157, TB-500)\n   • Cognitive / Mental Clarity (Semax, Selank, Dihexa)\n   • Hormone Optimization (Sermorelin, Ipamorelin/CJC-1295)\n   • Skin Rejuvenation \"Glow Stack\" (GHK-Cu, Glutathione)\n   • Metabolic / Body Comp (AOD-9604, MOTS-C, Tesamorelin)\n3. Lab work protocols (baseline & follow-up — Quest, Labcorp, or Evexia)\n4. Patient intake forms, health questionnaires & consent waivers (digital)\n5. Adverse event protocols & emergency procedures\n6. Prescriber workflow (consult → labs → prescribe → pharmacy ships → follow-up)\n7. Biomarker tracking & progress review templates",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "1. Peptide protocol library (dosing, cycling, contraindications, monitoring)\n2. Signature programs/stacks design:\n   • Weight Management (Tirzepatide or Semaglutide — 12-week program)\n   • Anti-Aging Stack (NAD+, GHK-Cu, Epithalon)\n   • Recovery \"Wolverine\" Stack (BPC-157, TB-500)\n   • Cognitive / Mental Clarity (Semax, Selank, Dihexa)\n   • Hormone Optimization (Sermorelin, Ipamorelin/CJC-1295)\n   • Skin Rejuvenation \"Glow Stack\" (GHK-Cu, Glutathione)\n   • Metabolic / Body Comp (AOD-9604, MOTS-C, Tesamorelin)\n3. Lab work protocols (baseline & follow-up — Quest, Labcorp, or Evexia)\n4. Patient intake forms, health questionnaires & consent waivers (digital)\n5. Adverse event protocols & emergency procedures\n6. Prescriber workflow (consult → labs → prescribe → pharmacy ships → follow-up)\n7. Biomarker tracking & progress review templates",
      "autoResize": true,
