    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "p3-items",
      "x": 80,
      "y": 888,
      "width": 750,
      "height": 220,
      "text": "1. Service menu & pricing (program-based, not a la carte — higher perceived value)\n2. Program tiers: Starter (single peptide), Signature (stacks), Premium (concierge)\n3. Subscription/membership model ($199-499/mo for ongoing protocols)\n4. Patient onboarding: book consult → intake → labs → video consult → Rx → ship\n5. Telehealth scheduling system (Calendly or built-in EHR scheduling)\n6. Payment processing + subscription billing (Stripe recurring, payment plans)\n7. Pharmacy fulfillment coordination (order mgmt, shipping tracking, refill reminders)\n8. Staffing plan (NPs/PAs for consults, patient care coordinator, admin)\n9. CRM / patient communication (email + SMS for check-ins, refills, lab follow-ups)",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "1. Service menu & pricing (program-based, not a la carte — higher perceived value)\n2. Program tiers: Starter (single peptide), Signature (stacks), Premium (concierge)\n3. Subscription/membership model ($199-499/mo for ongoing protocols)\n4. Patient onboarding: book consult → intake → labs → video consult → Rx → ship\n5. Telehealth scheduling system (Calendly or built-in EHR scheduling)\n6. Payment processing + subscription billing (Stripe recurring, payment plans)\n7. Pharmacy fulfillment coordination (order mgmt, shipping tracking, refill reminders)\n8. Staffing plan (NPs/PAs for consults, patient care coordinator, admin)\n9. CRM / patient communication (email + SMS for check-ins, refills, lab follow-ups)",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
