    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "p4-items",
      "x": 80,
      "y": 1198,
      "width": 750,
      "height": 180,
      "text": "1. Brand identity (luxury wellness / science-backed — gold/amber, clean, elevated)\n2. Website (education-heavy — peptide pages, program pages, \"How It Works\", booking)\n3. SEO strategy (\"peptide therapy near me\", \"semaglutide online\", \"BPC-157 benefits\")\n4. Social media (Instagram + TikTok — educational content, transformations, explainers)\n5. YouTube/long-form (peptide deep dives, \"What is BPC-157?\", weight loss journeys)\n6. Email nurture sequences (lead magnet → education series → book consult CTA)\n7. Trust signals (physician bios, pharmacy certs, testimonials, before/after results)\n8. Blog/content hub (SEO articles on each peptide, conditions, lifestyle optimization)",
