    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "p5-items",
      "x": 80,
      "y": 1468,
      "width": 750,
      "height": 220,
      "text": "1. Google Ads — \"semaglutide online\", \"peptide therapy\", \"tirzepatide\" (highest intent)\n2. Meta Ads — transformation stories, educational content, \"Are you a candidate?\" quiz\n3. Podcast appearances (biohacking, fitness, wellness, anti-aging podcasts)\n4. Influencer partnerships (fitness influencers, biohackers, wellness creators)\n5. Referral program ($100 credit for referrer, $50 off for friend)\n6. Strategic partnerships (functional medicine docs, chiropractors, trainers, gyms)\n7. Free educational webinars (\"Intro to Peptide Therapy\" — capture leads, build trust)\n8. Lead magnets (peptide guide PDF, \"Which Peptide Is Right For You?\" quiz)\n9. Affiliate program for healthcare practitioners (refer patients, earn commission)",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
