    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "p6-items",
      "x": 80,
      "y": 1808,
      "width": 750,
      "height": 210,
      "text": "1. Build recurring patient base (subscriptions are the engine — 200+ active monthly)\n2. Add high-ticket programs (12-week transformation $2,500-5,000, concierge $997/mo)\n3. Expand prescriber capacity (hire additional NPs/PAs for more consult slots)\n4. Multi-state licensing (expand to 10-20 states for larger addressable market)\n5. Add weight loss as gateway (Semaglutide/Tirzepatide = highest demand, easiest to market)\n6. Supplement/nutraceutical add-ons (private label or curated — $30-100/mo per patient)\n7. Corporate wellness / executive health packages\n8. Group programs / cohort-based transformations (accountability + community)\n9. White-label / B2B (license your protocols to other practitioners)",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "1. Build recurring patient base (subscriptions are the engine — 200+ active monthly)\n2. Add high-ticket programs (12-week transformation $2,500-5,000, concierge $997/mo)\n3. Expand prescriber capacity (hire additional NPs/PAs for more consult slots)\n4. Multi-state licensing (expand to 10-20 states for larger addressable market)\n5. Add weight loss as gateway (Semaglutide/Tirzepatide = highest demand, easiest to market)\n6. Supplement/nutraceutical add-ons (private label or curated — $30-100/mo per patient)\n7. Corporate wellness / executive health packages\n8. Group programs / cohort-based transformations (accountability + community)\n9. White-label / B2B (license your protocols to other practitioners)",
